description:
Alex Monaco shares his sports betting knowledge as he gives you the best bets to make at the Breeder's Cup and NFL Week 9. Monaco is joined by Simon Hunter of The Favorites who breaks down all the NFL action and Mike Joyce of FanDuel TV helps you make smart bets at the Breeder's Cup. #Volume #Herd #ColinCowherd
